    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《全民街篮》是一款全新的篮球竞技端游。在这里，没有复杂的规则束缚，只有酣畅淋漓的团队配合与实时较量；没有一成不变的套路，只有操作与策略的双重较量！打造属于你的“时尚潮流篮球明星”，用你的“炫酷操作”带领团队赢下每一场比赛。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383020/extras/a7a22924ea9c8906e85e2f317c360048.poster.avif?t=1766546728\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383020/extras/a7a22924ea9c8906e85e2f317c360048.webm?t=1766546728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383020/extras/a7a22924ea9c8906e85e2f317c360048.mp4?t=1766546728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >策略：有策略 不单调 首款战术竞技街篮端游</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《全民街篮》创新性地将MOBA玩法与传统街篮竞技相融合！玩家可以通过各类系统提升球员能力，塑造符合自己操作习惯与战术偏好的角色。灵活选择不同球员，搭配个性化的养成路线，合理运用专属天赋与比赛策略，将让你在比赛中占据主动，感受角色养成与战术竞技的完美结合！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383020/extras/cc265221e8e28417710c384ffae52a12.poster.avif?t=1766546728\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383020/extras/cc265221e8e28417710c384ffae52a12.webm?t=1766546728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383020/extras/cc265221e8e28417710c384ffae52a12.mp4?t=1766546728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >潮酷：新潮酷 新街头 时尚嘻哈自定义</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >延续街头篮球的“自由”精神，《全民街篮》融入国潮、赛博朋克、复古朋克等多元化元素，演绎独特的街头嘻哈风格。玩家可以通皮肤、球场装饰、花式动作、专属篮球等模块，打造专属于自己的篮球潮流，彰显个性，成为赛场上最吸睛的存在！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383020/extras/15cb473e7f15c771dcdfb3a826ec7f02.poster.avif?t=1766546728\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383020/extras/15cb473e7f15c771dcdfb3a826ec7f02.webm?t=1766546728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383020/extras/15cb473e7f15c771dcdfb3a826ec7f02.mp4?t=1766546728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >操作：低门槛 有深度 爽快的操作手感</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《全民街篮》全面优化了操作体验，既保留了资深玩家所追求的操作深度，又降低了门槛，让新手玩家也能轻松上手。无论是精准投篮、突破上篮，还是酷炫扣篮，都能通过简单的操作实现，让每一位玩家都能享受到篮球竞技的独特魅力。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383020/extras/5cacc1330704ebbb4f726ef99b14f711.poster.avif?t=1766546728\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383020/extras/5cacc1330704ebbb4f726ef99b14f711.webm?t=1766546728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383020/extras/5cacc1330704ebbb4f726ef99b14f711.mp4?t=1766546728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >团队：强配合 真畅快 畅享团队篮球魅力</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，篮球不再是一个人的游戏，而是团队之间的默契对抗！流畅的传球、精准的跑位、极具冲击力的配合战术，每一个细节都可能决定胜负。与队友一起沟通、协作，用你的团队配合Carry全场，体验酣畅淋漓的篮球竞技乐趣！</p>",
